---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Freedom Mobility NY | Home Accessibility Experts Rochester Buffalo Syracuse"
  description="Locally owned and operated since serving NY families. Expert stairlifts, ramps & lifts in Rochester, Buffalo and Syracuse. Free consultations and professional installation."
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <span class="uppercase tracking-[2px] text-sky-600 text-sm">WHO WE ARE</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter mt-2 mb-6">About Freedom Mobility NY</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-slate text-[15.2px] text-slate-700">
        <p>
          At Freedom Mobility NY, we believe everyone deserves the freedom to move comfortably and safely in their own home. 
          Based in Rochester, we serve the greater Rochester, Buffalo, and Syracuse areas, helping individuals with mobility challenges 
          regain independence through expertly designed accessibility solutions.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our team of dedicated professionals is passionate about making a difference, offering personalized service from 
          free in-home consultations to professional installation and ongoing support.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-2xl tracking-tight mb-6">Our Commitment</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Customer-First Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Your satisfaction is our priority. We listen first, then deliver solutions that truly fit your life and home.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Expertise You Can Trust</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Our technicians are highly trained and experienced with a wide range of stairlifts, ramps, lifts, and home modifications.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white border rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Community Focus</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">We’re proud to serve New York residents with care and respect. We live and work in the communities we serve.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10">
      <p class="italic text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-prose">
        “Locally owned and operated you can rest easy knowing that we are only a phone call away!”
      </p>
      <div class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-500">— The Freedom Mobility NY Team</div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a href="/testimonials" class="text-sm underline text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700">Read more real stories from clients in our area →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
